data.description: ONE OF A KIND HOME! Captivating 2-bdrm (or 3) home sits on hill above downtown, where costal living meets urban charm. It offers a perfect blend of convenience & tranquility. Step inside to be greeted by the timeless allure of hardwood floors that stretch seamlessly throughout the entire living space, bathed in natural light. Breathtaking views of bay & mountains from upper deck, ideal spot to savor morning coffee or host unforgettable gatherings. Small loft area provides a cozy retreat, perfect for reading or home office. The real treasure is location situated in the heart of Pt Orchard. Easy access to restaurants, shops & entertainment. The views make every day feel like a vacation. Don't miss your chance to own this delightful property.
